{"tid":1446713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候搞番和理非大遊行！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:57.000Z","uid":63222,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"627a48dcad6c13cf4e25bb492b8fa6e115454b03","tid":1446713,"uid":63222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"不得不承認     早排因為罷工同不合作運動民意流失左少少<br />\n但見到今日又向地鐵站射彈又射爆人隻眼<br />\n係時候聚集番民意再同和理非connect<br />\n更重要既係將游離既民意再聚起來<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都知和理非遊行冇乜用   <br />\n但呢個絕對係令中立游離歸隊既好機會<br />\n<br />\n愈原始愈根本既訴求愈易聚民意<br />\n反對警隊過份暴力呢種可以喚醒一般市民最根本既在共鳴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政治唔單止係保留自己既支持者<br />\n更加係要令未/唔支持既人支持自己</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油  <br />\n呢場仗仲要打好耐</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請善用不推文回覆垃圾post 三毛post由佢沉<br />\n集中討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEjUScN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEjUScN.png&h=c18a0f59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQJeScO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQJeScO.png&h=19aecac1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnT6Jju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnT6Jju.png&h=24592c53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba2d6634b78e1c36a41cb60e74b6aa7bc0e1df52","tid":1446713,"uid":63222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"85a947182e2832ed87a76a39ab7f5f0f9e58924d","tid":1446713,"uid":63222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply